# LOTW replay fixture v1
# Format:
#   frame <count> [buttons...]
# Buttons use these names: up down left right A B start select.
#
# This fixture waits for the title prompt, starts the game, then holds right
# long enough to exercise early player-control code. It stores only controller
# timing, not ROM data or captured frames.
frame 300
frame 12 start
frame 180
frame 180 right
frame 60
